Irish Red Ale (10.5 gal)

Maltaat:
12.0 lbs Maris Otter
4.0 lbs Vienna
12.0 oz Roast Barley
6.0 oz Crystal Malt (120L)

Humalat:
2.0 oz Fuggles  (4.5%AA)
1.0 oz Goldings  (5.0%AA)

Muut ainekset:

Ohjeet:
Recipe Type: All Grain
Yeast: Wyeast 1272
Yeast Starter: 1.25L x2
Original Gravity: 1.051
Final Gravity: 1.011
IBU: 21
Mash: 75 min @ 150F
Boiling Time (Minutes): 60
2 oz Fuggles @ 60 min
1 oz Goldings @ 15 min
Primary Fermentation (# of Days & Temp): 10 @65*F
Secondary Fermentation (# of Days & Temp): 14 @72*F

Muistiinpanoja:
Color: Ruby red
Tasting Notes: Roasty, malt forward but dry finish. Modeled after Smithwicks, 
the "gold standard"